Corporate Events
The Hut
Need a break from the boardroom? The Hut offers a unique and relaxed setting that’s perfect for corporate events with a twist. Whether it’s a team-building session, networking mixer, or a casual company celebration, this cozy tropical space blends laid-back vibes with just the right amount of professionalism. With room to gather, present, and connect, The Hut makes work feel a little more like play.
The Poolside
Set against the lush backdrop of Golden Host Resort, the Poolside area offers a refreshing and inspiring venue for your next corporate event. Whether it’s a company mixer, team celebration, or client appreciation night, this open-air space blends casual elegance with tropical charm. With the pool glistening nearby and plenty of room to network, unwind, and connect, your event will feel less like work—and more like a well-earned escape.
